{"tid":1272261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[皇帝唔急太監急] 陳雲：今日警方聰明，保持克制，由黨衛軍梁張朱鄺郭遊說建國義民撤兵。","createTime":"2019-07-01T09:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T11:15:52.000Z","uid":131171,"like":28,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b34b6c78a08ee56dfbc645ac1041e770cbd1562","tid":1272261,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"陳雲：今日警方聰明，保持克制，由黨衛軍出動。黨衛軍梁耀忠、張超雄、朱凱迪、鄺俊宇、郭家麒遊說建國義民撤兵。收效了。<br />\n義民可以抵抗一隊裝備精良的警察，反而抵擋不住幾個老弱的黨衛軍。<br />\n革命，從來是思想的問題，心理的障礙，多於動員與武裝的問題。你思想殘缺，給你肩托式榴彈砲，你也會交回給泛民，之後入去監牢十年。<br />\n搞好思想問題，再出來吧。一隊痴線的兵團，入精神病院好過，上前線把撚呀。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：<span style=\"color: red;\">泛民才是香港建國的最大障礙，不是港共，是泛民。各位清楚見到，泛民才是共產黨的黨衛軍。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjsxkdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjsxkdE.jpg&h=85d6215f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b94515df1eff561de8a6e408e9f8c8160b92a90","tid":1272261,"uid":131171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"陳雲：政治對答。<br />\nH.N: 可有辦法俾美國知道泛民班人吃裹扒外，佢哋嘅所作所為已背叛美國。<br />\nWan Chin: 無囉。革命軍團這麼尊敬泛民，證明泛民也是香港義民的代表，有最廣泛的代表性，美國不找泛民談，找誰呢？<span style=\"color: red;\">義民出擊，結果竟然是幫泛民拉票，被他們領取了和平解散、恢復秩序的大功勞，義民做來把撚呀？返屋企撚狗玩貓好過啦。</span>"},{"pid":"e2530bbf8ba0093279046aa9f073af3816af4c45","tid":1272261,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b605fe3936db88ea511adbe8c569dba570b55e41","tid":1272261,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"趙雲又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1024580218b57f08f1fbd89942c0d97834a0e68d","tid":1272261,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50ab561474ba61986c930fc60f543e22ce6fbf2","tid":1272261,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bbc8085f445a8952a0e83badbd61ed03bbc3bf","tid":1272261,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6472412955f890f82a899cff30f521cc023e35","tid":1272261,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d473c5d832a66ed79201b00d60ef34ace1c68aa","tid":1272261,"uid":4050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，屌嗰啲當然90%都係五毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，呢個就係拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟，共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持清醒，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易上五毛當"},{"pid":"0f0d6729a145a126a8686b8b4cd098aa930efda3","tid":1272261,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"原來入到立法會就可以建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4181dc89278b40e0bf22e9f0bf74ffb24ee6f2b4","tid":1272261,"uid":159216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"無講錯"},{"pid":"28e052f5eb8ccbbfab4bd6ceaa941c236ca70d2a","tid":1272261,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{